{"Sid":0,"Did":118133,"Id":"282281","Title":"羅東孔子廟孔子塑像","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collection/cf124898-5ff5-4da5-bb58-8c9ae68d0f67/108-her-pa-1815-201910252332445db2e16a5063c0.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n羅東孔子廟原於1900（明治33）年創建於今羅東鎮日新戲院址，1967年遷建現址，臨北成路入口建有牌樓與禮門義路。進入後有一水池，或有泮池之意。水池之後與大成殿之間，則安奉有一尊白色孔子塑像。此孔子像真人等身全身像，其形象較近似唐代吳道子所繪「先師孔子行教像」，未戴冠帽，僅著布巾，雙手於胸前略往上疊握；左脅下可見佩有長劍，乃沿襲自春秋時期，士者皆佩劍之慣習。此孔子像乃立於梯形基座上，四邊施以孔子周遊列國講學之淺浮雕。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.7616665","Keyword_Latitude":"24.6752922","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/C75AB4C8-1430-426E-8A82-0D8C951DE6EF","Original_Identifier":"282281","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"孔子 / 文宗社 / 羅東孔子廟","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 15:12:16","timelines":"","place":"羅東鎮羅東孔子廟","address":"宜蘭縣羅東鎮北成路一段26號","longitude":"121.7616665","latitude":"24.6752922","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"","writer":"葉永韶/ 蔡明志","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collectionOpen/e16c07fe-db13-4241-a754-669ad9ddfbfc/108-her-pa-1815-re-201910252333535db2e16a5063c0.jpg"}}